\c 22
\p
\v 1 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakati: Iyi iimba yaJehovha Mwari, uye iyi iaritari yechipo chinopiswa chaIsraeri.
\s Dhavhidhi anogadzira zvekuvaka tembere nazvo
\p
\v 2 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakaraira kuunganidza vatorwa vaiva panyika yaIsraeri; ndokugadza vavezi vemabwe, kuti vaveze mabwe akagadzirwa kuvaka imba yaMwari.
\v 3 Dhavhidhi akagadzirawo matare mazhinji ezvipikiri zvemagonhi emikova neekubatanidza; uye ndarira zhinji isina \add kuyerwa\add* uremu.
\v 4 Nematanda emisidhari asina kuverengwa; nokuti VaZidhoni neVaTire vakauya nemisidhari mizhinji kwazvo kuna Dhavhidhi.
\v 5 Dhavhidhi ndokuti: Soromoni mwanakomana wangu mudiki asina simba, uye imba ichavakirwa Jehovha, inofanira kuva huru kwazvo pazita neparumbidzo panyika dzese; ndichaigadzirira hangu. Dhavhidhi ndokugadzira zvizhinji asati afa.
\p
\v 6 Zvino wakadana Soromoni mwanakomana wake, ndokumuraira kuvakira Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri imba.
\v 7 Dhavhidhi ndokuti kuna Soromoni: Mwanakomana wangu: Kana ndiri ini, zvaiva mumoyo wangu kuvakira zita raJehovha Mwari wangu imba.
\v 8 Asi shoko raJehovha rakasvika kwandiri, richiti: Wakateura ropa zhinji kwazvo, uye wakaita dzihondo dzakakura; zvino haungavakiri zita rangu imba, nokuti wakateura ropa zhinji panyika pamberi pangu.
\v 9 Tarira, uchaberekerwa mwanakomana, achava munhu wezororo; uye ndichamupa zororo kubva pavavengi vake vese vakapoteredza; nokuti zita rake richava Soromoni, uye ndichapa rugare nerunyararo kuna Israeri mumazuva ake.
\v 10 Iye achavakira zita rangu imba; uye achava mwanakomana wangu, neni \add ndichava\add* baba vake. Zvino ndichasimbisa chigaro chake cheushe pamusoro paIsraeri kusvika rinhi narinhi.
\v 11 Ikozvino, mwanakomana wangu, Jehovha ngaave newe; uye ubudirire ugovaka imba yaJehovha Mwari wako, sekutaura kwake pamusoro pako.
\v 12 Koga Jehovha ngaakupe njere nekunzwisisa, agokuraira pamusoro paIsraeri; kuti uchengete murairo waJehovha Mwari wako.
\v 13 Ipapo uchabudirira, kana uchichenjerera kuzadzisa zvimiso nemitongo Jehovha zvaakaraira Mozisi nazvo maererano naIsraeri, simba uve neushingi, usatya, kana kuodzwa moyo.
\v 14 Zvino tarira, pakutambudzika kwangu ndagadzirira imba yaJehovha matarenda zvuru zana zvegoridhe, nematarenda churu chezvuru esirivha; nendarira nematare zvisina \add kuyerwa\add* uremu, nokuti zvizhinji kwazvo; uye matanda nemabwe ndagadzira. Zvino uchawedzera kwazviri.
\v 15 Uye vashandi vazhinji unavo, vavezi vemabwe nenyanzwi dzemabwe nematanda, nemurume umwe neumwe wakachenjera pabasa ripi neripi;
\v 16 nepagoridhe, nesirivha, nendarira, nematare hapana \add kuyerwa\add* uwandu. Simuka ushande, Jehovha ave newe.
\p
\v 17 Dhavhidhi wakarairawo misoro yese yaIsraeri kubatsira Soromoni mwanakomana wake, \add akati\add*:
\v 18 Jehovha Mwari wenyu haasi nemwi here? Uye haana kukupai zororo kudivi rimwe nerimwe here? Nokuti wakapa vagari venyika muruoko rwangu, uye nyika yakaiswa pasi pamberi paJehovha nepamberi pevanhu vake.
\v 19 Ikozvino misai moyo yenyu nemweya yenyu kutsvaka Jehovha Mwari wenyu. Simukai zvino muvake nzvimbo tsvene yaJehovha Mwari, kupinza areka yesungano yaJehovha nenhumbi tsvene dzaMwari muimba yakavakirwa zita raJehovha.